dcterms:creator: Vitaly Feldman
dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of circuits with at most n^0.99 gates, where each gate computes any function computable by a polynomial threshold function of degree k.
dcterms:title: Circuits of at most n^0.99 gates (Class 1)

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of decision trees with at most n^0.99 depth, where each node computes a query by a polynomial threshold function of degree k.
dcterms:title: Decision trees of at most n^0.99 depth (Class 2)

dcterms:creator: Vitaly Feldman
dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of circuits with at most n^(1−ε) gates, where each gate computes any function computable by a SYM+ circuit of size 2^nζ and degree k.
dcterms:title: Circuits of at most n^(1−ε) gates (Class 3)

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of decision trees with at most n^(1−ε) depth, where each node computes a query by a size 2^nζ SYM+ circuit.
dcterms:title: Decision trees of at most n^(1−ε) depth (Class 4)
